data.description: Back On market buyer could not perform!*Minutes to Belford Seastreek ferry W/ service to NYC!!* Gorgeous 4 bedroom Bi-Level home in the heart of Belford. Set amongst a park like lot with a HUGE backyard inclusive of a brand new fire-pit. Located on a cul-de-sac. Hardwood floors throughout. Stunning upgraded kitchen cabinets & designer stainless steel appliances. Kitchen provides access to outside deck. 3 nice sized bedrooms upstairs. Downstairs has additional 4th bedroom W/ ability to add a 2nd bathroom- perfect for guests! Media room sure to WOW you features a theatre set up & wood burning fireplace. This room also leads to the back yard W/ new Pavers & 2 fire pit areas! Whether you love to entertain or enjoy the peace and serenity of your home - this home is perfect !
